about.summary: A python package for non-parametric Mann-Kendall family of trend tests.

name: pymannkendall
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pymannkendall" %}
{% set version = "1.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a10a1cc24c7466bce7e1c0c70c5601ad44aee573d2ce161e6e68b60f6a94e11e

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
    - scipy
  run:
    - numpy
    - python
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - pymannkendall

about:
  home: https://github.com/mmhs013/pymannkendall
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A python package for non-parametric Mann-Kendall family of trend tests.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dpryan79
